messages.messageBody:
Hey Suzan! I didn't know you were on this list. :0)
Nice to see someone else from ME. You might try posting for a violin on
one of the Maine lists. You never know.

Hey, I was wondering the other day if we have finished our subscription
to Life Learning. Do you know if you have received 6 copies yet?

Angela in Maine

-----Original Message-----
From: szdmmtt [mailto:szdmmtt@...]
Sent: Wednesday, April 02, 2003 7:49 AM
To: Unschooling-dotcom@yahoogroups.com
Subject: [Unschooling-dotcom] used 3/4 size violin wanted


We live in Auburn Maine and are looking for a used 3/4 size violin
with bow and case. If anyone has one you can contact us at
szdmmtt@... with price. We are willing to travel up to 60 miles.
Thanks
